title: Sky Break v3.0
description:
Humanity is threatened. A mortal virus awoke, and it is spreading quickly.
The particular flora of Arcania, a planet used to prepare humans for space colonization, may help in the creation of a cure. But it is now abandoned since working drones turned against humans.
A group of researchers is sent to this planet to find a solution. You are one of them.
